{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Enter: Akatsuki, The Ninja!\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4 - A Friendly Gathering (Part 2)<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Ikazuchi and Inazuma invited Akatsuki and me to come and play a game, Fleet Fighter V, that they had borrowed from Long Island.","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_room","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Take that!","actor":301110,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"W-what in the?! Oh no!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Alright, let's wreck some face!","dir":1,"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"side":2,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"→↘↓↙←→+BD↓+CC↓↙←→+CD, ↘←↙↓↘→←↓↙+BC, →↓←＋P＋G→←＋P＋G→←＋P＋G←↓→↑←＋P＋G↓→←＋P!","dir":1,"flashN":{"alpha":[[0,1,0.2],[1,0,0.2,0.2],[0,1,0.2,0.4],[1,0,0.2,0.6]],"color":[1,1,1]},"side":2,"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... What just happened?","actor":301090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"K.O., flawless victory. Inazuma and Ikazuchi defeated us again.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Even in a 2v1, we can't beat Ikazuchi... I-I mean, I'm just not familiar with the controls, that's all!","actor":301090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Heheheh! You'd need TAS-like reaction speeds to beat me!","actor":301110,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The final score was 10-0 for Ikazuchi.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.4,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Phew... I see! Games can be really fun!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.4,"dur":0.4,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"However, it's not good to get addicted to them. Please tell her about the dangers of getting hooked on gaming, Akatsuki.","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301120},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"......","actor":301090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"(Whispering) If only Hibiki were here...","actor":301090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Akatsuki? Is something the matter?","actor":301120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"N-nothing at all! I was just thinking out loud...","actor":301090,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"About Hibiki?","actor":301120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'm certain she's all right. Sometimes it's best not to worry about things like this. I'm sure the Commander agrees.","dir":1,"side":0,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"......"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301120},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Is it...? ... I'm feeling somewhat tired, so I think I'll go home now...","dir":1,"side":1,"action":[{"x":1500,"dur":1,"type":"move","y":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What's wrong, Akatsuki?","actor":301110,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"It seems like Inazuma's attempt to reassure Akatsuki didn't have any effect.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"That got me thinking... Maybe Hibiki is the reason why Akatsuki's been reading the patrol reports so thoroughly every day...","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"XIAO4","fadeOut":1.5}